http://www.thehindu.com/news/international/3000-killed-in-Russian-airstrikes-in-Syria-since-Sept./article14010144.ece

At least 3,000 people, including more than 1,000 civilians, have been killed in Russian air strikes in Syria since September 30, a monitoring group said on Wednesday.The Syrian Observatory for Human Rights, which monitors the violence in the country through a wide network of local sources, said that 893 Islamic State members were among those killed in the strikes.